{"tid":1909423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日跳閘之前見到有個絲打捐閘","createTime":"2020-03-04T02:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T10:50:03.000Z","uid":198595,"like":120,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"25b39b500654bf0bd388b4acb9fc1c0fe35b63e3","tid":1909423,"uid":198595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T02:58:04.000Z","msg":"我一行到附近見到你望左下左右然後捐左閘<br />\n跟住見到你好似勁驚咁走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我係後面都跳左閘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好耐都無見到有巴絲打跳或捐了成日得我一個咁做<br />\n然後你一搭上去我見到你望我就比左個like既手勢你<br />\n見到你好似覺得比人踢爆勁尷尬咁覺得超好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知你會唔會見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比多十個like你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWell done<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7af9d72c63162052a53d9c820c14c58d90ace6","tid":1909423,"uid":174120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T02:58:48.000Z","msg":"做得好"},{"pid":"ae4f18b85ed325235cf130bffb194ff5ae63342d","tid":1909423,"uid":167506,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T02:59:16.000Z","msg":"仲搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff12786